  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\u003carticle data-post-id=\"805445\"\u003e\n\n    \u003cheader\u003e\n          \n    \n\n        \n  \u003c/header\u003e\n      \n  \n\n  \u003cdiv\u003e\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n      \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_805449\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-805449\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/?attachment_id=805449\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-805449\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg data-perfmatters-preload=\"\" fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/04_lefevre_rgb-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"A group of people hike in a snowy, mountainous landscape toward a large, circular, stone-like structure embedded in the snow, with overcast skies and rugged terrain surrounding them.\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/04_lefevre_rgb-800x534.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/04_lefevre_rgb-320x213.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/04_lefevre_rgb-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/04_lefevre_rgb-450x300.jpg 450w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/04_lefevre_rgb-300x200.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/04_lefevre_rgb-120x80.jpg 120w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/04_lefevre_rgb.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-805449\"\u003eForm \u003cem\u003eVertur: Frozen Landscapes of Iceland\u003c/em\u003e by Patrick Lefèvre\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003cp\u003e“Vetur” means “winter” in Icelandic — a season during which weather and light can change in the blink of an eye, reshaping vast open spaces into visions of fleeting magic or quiet desolation. \u003c/p\u003e  \u003cp\u003ePatrick Lefèvre’s photographs embrace this duality. In often desert-like landscapes where the road becomes the thread of life, he traces a path through snowbound expanses and glacial silence, capturing moments of both transcendence and austerity.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_805448\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-805448\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/?attachment_id=805448\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-805448\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/03_lefevre_rgb-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"A wide waterfall cascades into a blue river surrounded by snow-covered rocks and a white, wintry landscape under a bright, overcast sky.\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/03_lefevre_rgb-800x534.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/03_lefevre_rgb-320x213.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/03_lefevre_rgb-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/03_lefevre_rgb-450x300.jpg 450w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/03_lefevre_rgb-300x200.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/03_lefevre_rgb-120x80.jpg 120w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/03_lefevre_rgb.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-805448\"\u003ePatrick Lefèvre\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_805447\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-805447\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/?attachment_id=805447\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-805447\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/02_lefevre_rgb-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"A snowy, white landscape with a cloud of steam or smoke rising from the ground, possibly from a hot spring or geyser, under an overcast sky. The scene appears cold and desolate.\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/02_lefevre_rgb-800x534.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/02_lefevre_rgb-320x213.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/02_lefevre_rgb-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/02_lefevre_rgb-450x300.jpg 450w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/02_lefevre_rgb-300x200.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/02_lefevre_rgb-120x80.jpg 120w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/02_lefevre_rgb.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-805447\"\u003ePatrick Lefèvre\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_805446\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-805446\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/?attachment_id=805446\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-805446\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/01_lefevre_rgb-800x532.jpg\" alt=\"Several people walk and stand on a vast, snowy, and icy landscape surrounded by ice formations and patches of scattered snow under a bright, overcast sky.\" width=\"800\" height=\"532\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/01_lefevre_rgb-800x532.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/01_lefevre_rgb-320x213.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/01_lefevre_rgb-1536x1021.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/01_lefevre_rgb-450x300.jpg 450w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/01_lefevre_rgb-300x200.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/01_lefevre_rgb-120x80.jpg 120w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/01_lefevre_rgb.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-805446\"\u003ePatrick Lefèvre\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_805451\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-805451\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/?attachment_id=805451\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-805451\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/07_lefevre_rgb-533x800.jpg\" alt=\"A snow-covered, rocky landscape with rolling hills and a winding road bordered by a fence, all shrouded in heavy snowfall and mist, creating a cold and desolate atmosphere.\" width=\"533\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/07_lefevre_rgb-533x800.jpg 533w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/07_lefevre_rgb-213x320.jpg 213w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/07_lefevre_rgb.jpg 666w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 533px) 100vw, 533px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-805451\"\u003ePatrick Lefèvre\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n \u003cp\u003eWinters in Iceland can be both mercilessly cold and incredibly beautiful. The rapidly changing weather and light conditions of the winter months transform this quiet, remote country into a true natural spectacle. \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eIn February 2024, Lefèvre explored Iceland for the first time. The photographer artfully used the unique Icelandic light, with its high contrasts and the magical atmosphere of the isolated, snow-covered environment, to create a sensitive reality in his images. \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eThe landscapes are almost desert-like, with roads as the only lifeline. The photographs span a wide range of iconic and lesser-known Icelandic locations — from the crater lake Kerio and the volcanic Katla region to the dramatic Dettifoss waterfall and the mist-covered peninsulas of Snaefellsnes and Reykjanes. \u003c/p\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_805453\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-805453\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/?attachment_id=805453\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-805453\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/09_lefevre_rgb-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"Snow-covered mountain peaks under an overcast sky, with rugged slopes and rocky ridges partially obscured by mist and snow. The scene appears cold and serene.\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/09_lefevre_rgb-800x534.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/09_lefevre_rgb-320x213.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/09_lefevre_rgb-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/09_lefevre_rgb-450x300.jpg 450w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/09_lefevre_rgb-300x200.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/09_lefevre_rgb-120x80.jpg 120w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/09_lefevre_rgb.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-805453\"\u003ePatrick Lefèvre\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_805452\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-805452\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/?attachment_id=805452\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-805452\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/08_lefevre_rgb-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"A snowy coastline with rocky outcrops meets the cold sea under a cloudy sky. A fence runs along the foreground, and the landscape appears windswept and desolate.\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/08_lefevre_rgb-800x534.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/08_lefevre_rgb-320x213.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/08_lefevre_rgb-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/08_lefevre_rgb-450x300.jpg 450w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/08_lefevre_rgb-300x200.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/08_lefevre_rgb-120x80.jpg 120w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/08_lefevre_rgb.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-805452\"\u003ePatrick Lefèvre\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_805450\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-805450\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/?attachment_id=805450\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-805450\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/05_lefevre_rgb-800x534.jpg\" alt=\"A snowy, mountainous landscape with scattered rocks and groups of people walking in the distance. The scene is dominated by white snow, with mountains rising in the background under an overcast sky.\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/05_lefevre_rgb-800x534.jpg 800w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/05_lefevre_rgb-320x213.jpg 320w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/05_lefevre_rgb-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/05_lefevre_rgb-450x300.jpg 450w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/05_lefevre_rgb-300x200.jpg 300w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/05_lefevre_rgb-120x80.jpg 120w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/05_lefevre_rgb.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-805450\"\u003ePatrick Lefèvre\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e \u003cfigure id=\"attachment_805454\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-805454\"\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://petapixel.com/?attachment_id=805454\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-805454\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/10_lefevre_rgb-534x800.jpg\" alt=\"Snow-covered hillside with scattered trees reflected in a calm, icy lake under a pale, overcast sky.\" width=\"534\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/10_lefevre_rgb-534x800.jpg 534w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/10_lefevre_rgb-213x320.jpg 213w, https://petapixel.com/assets/uploads/2025/07/10_lefevre_rgb.jpg 667w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 534px) 100vw, 534px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption id=\"caption-attachment-805454\"\u003ePatrick Lefèvre\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n \u003cp\u003eYet, Lefèvre avoids postcard realism. His Iceland is not about spectacle, but about essence. Each image pares the landscape down to its quiet core: a horizon blurred by fog, a single dark stone punctuating a white field, or a strip of road vanishing into light. Vetur. \u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eFrozen Landscapes of Iceland\u003c/em\u003e is more than a simple travel album or landscape book — the images unfold into a poetic visual story in which each photograph could stand on its own as a striking painting. Drawing inspiration from the aesthetics of Pictorialism, the photographs possess a painterly softness, balancing light and tone with minimalist precision. Their restrained palette and open compositions evoke a contemplative state — more like meditations than documentation. The result is a book that invites slowness, reflecting interior landscapes as much as the Icelandic terrain: a search for stillness, simplicity, and connection in a fragmented world.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eFrozen Landscapes of Iceland\u003c/em\u003e is \u003ca href=\"https://www.kehrerverlag.com/en/patrick-lefevre-vetur-frozen-landscapes-of-iceland-978-3-96900-190-5\" data-wpel-link=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"follow external noopener\"\u003epublished by Kehrer Verlag.\u003c/a\u003e \u003c/p\u003e      \u003c/div\u003e\n\n          \n      \n\n              \u003cdiv\u003e\n          \u003cp\u003ePetaPixel ar